{"tid":1160060,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"施榮懷：王志民稱如不設追溯期　立例後會赦免一大批罪犯","createTime":"2019-05-18T07:40:47.000Z","updateTime":"2019-05-19T05:35:38.000Z","uid":47714,"like":5,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":4,"replies":[{"pid":"75b6c3cdf5bbd9f05412a9e2653afc46889e04e8","tid":1160060,"uid":47714,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-18T07:40:47.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1458095-20190517.htm\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1458095-20190517.htm&d=vM7vEUXlfhstYrouAjV2ftRt30ToQ9uN2xIpFOlVN1U%3D&h=07a0b9fd\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1458095-20190517.htm&h=cc44e7c6\" target=\"_blank\">https://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1458095-20190517.htm</a><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/z9kXy8n.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fz9kXy8n.jpg&h=2c63b0b7&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n多名人大和政協下午到中聯辦與主任王志民會面，全國政協委員、香港中華廠商會永遠名譽會長施榮懷，在會後引述王志民說修訂《逃犯條例》需要有追溯期，以及不可設立日落條款。<br />\n<br />\n施榮懷說，王志民認為如果不設追溯期，在立例後就會馬上赦免一大批罪犯，連一個罪犯都不能遣返。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/HK.NationFront/photos/a.1660705024171201/2353656534876043/?type=3\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2FHK.NationFront%2Fphotos%2Fa.1660705024171201%2F2353656534876043%2F%3Ftype%3D3&d=vM7vEUXlfhstYrouAjV2ftRt30ToQ9uN2xIpFOlVN1U%3D&h=3d5d21fa\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.facebook.com/HK.NationFront/photos/a.1660705024171201/2353656534876043/?type=3</a><br />\n<br />\n【先定罪後立法】<br />\n<br />\n法未立，香港人在中共眼中已經是一大批罪犯了，就差有能力抓跟沒能力抓而已。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\nPearce Kwa:<br />\n中共咁急立法，看來真的貿易戰打到彈盡了⋯<br />\n<br />\nGary Li:<br />\n早排有人話咩「西環放風」話支共冇諗過搞呢壇嘢，係香港政府主意。信支共講嘢不如自己用個腦諗。"},{"pid":"9ee62f34da9a92dd5a58745ea9c576e2fe060c89","tid":1160060,"uid":47714,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-19T05:10:27.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"fe0386387fcf6b8d3d5839dae9794e27cb0d7cb2","tid":1160060,"uid":100347,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-19T05:15:21.000Z","msg":"收皮啦屌你老母<br />\n仲信糖衣毒藥咩<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6a6cafbb944ad716ebe64fca1f8f1f1e3a5d700d","tid":1160060,"uid":173002,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-19T05:23:33.000Z","msg":"王志民「<span style=\"color: brown;\">認為</span>」如果不設追溯期，在立例後就會馬上赦免<br />\n這個「認為」擺明係用個人名義引班商家佬入死局，改例後黨就以強國司法獨立法律嚴明為理由唔認數。<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"15b02f85899f6e94149bd64b633915d501de3bce","tid":1160060,"uid":166474,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-19T05:35:38.000Z","msg":"點解普通法地區可以有追溯期？"}]}